{
  "texts": [
    "SNPs were filtered based on parameters previously used [8].",
    "Population genetic structure was analyzed using the program ADMIX-TURE v1.23 [66] with the putative number of populations (K values) from two to six.",
    "A maximum likelihood-based phylogenetic tree analysis was performed using IQ-TREE v1.6.6 [67].",
    "Principal component analysis (PCA) was performed as previously described [8].",
    "The nucleotide diversity (π) was calculated using VCFtools in 20-kb sliding windows with a 10-kb step."
  ]
}